WEBVTT

00:11:29.732 --> 00:11:33.200
if you ritualize the transition
from work to home,

00:11:33.224 --> 00:11:35.938
and if you train yourself
to convert ruminations

00:11:35.962 --> 00:11:38.095
into productive forms of thinking,

00:11:38.119 --> 00:11:39.269
you will succeed.

00:11:39.950 --> 00:11:43.450
Banishing ruminations
truly enhanced my personal life,

00:11:43.474 --> 00:11:46.156
but what it enhanced even more

00:11:46.180 --> 00:11:49.688
was the joy and satisfaction
I get from my work.

00:11:50.442 --> 00:11:54.029
Ground zero for creating
a healthy work-life balance

00:11:54.053 --> 00:11:56.014
is not in the real world.

00:11:56.038 --> 00:11:57.442
It's in our head.

00:11:57.466 --> 00:11:58.866
It's with ruminating.

00:11:59.276 --> 00:12:03.149
If you want to reduce your stress
and improve your quality of life,